{{see|quién}}

== Spanish ==
===Etymology===
Latin ''[[quem|quĕm]]'', accusative of ''[[qui]]''

=== Pronoun ===
'''quien''' ''plural,'' '''quienes'''
# [[who]]; [[whom]]
#: ''¿Con [[quién]] hablo?'' - "With whom am I speaking?"
# [[whoever]]; [[whomever]]
#: ''[[Quien]] quiere hablar que habla.'' - "Whoever wants to speak may do so."
# [[anyone]]; some people
'''de quien'''
# [[whose]]
#: ''¿De [[quién]] es este?'' - "Whose is this?"
=== Usage note ===
Written with an accent mark (i.e. ''quién'') when interrogative.

